{"tid":706392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[聽住先] 中學者：美國會大選後 將「放開手腳制裁中國」","createTime":"2018-06-17T22:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T11:07:34.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da26ac68b3025f6a168690e49be0e486bf8fda9b","tid":706392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T22:53:53.000Z","msg":"中學者：美國會大選後 將「放開手腳制裁中國」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2461134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2461134&d=%2FO3HsluWmFOAV2OYkmdD8tr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=97536884\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2461134&h=b4e45f7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2461134</a><br />\n<br />\n〔編譯孫宇青／綜合報導〕美國總統川普近日宣布對中國500億美元、共1102項商品加徵25％關稅，立即遭到中國採取報復性反制措施。針對愈演愈烈的美中貿易戰，中國人民大學國際關係學院學者王義桅向香港「明報」表示，美中都在釋放信號試探對方反應，這股態勢到年底美國國會大選前都不會停止，美方還有可能在大選後「放開手腳全方位壓制中國」。<br />\n<br />\n王義桅指出，美中兩國的貿易戰半年來一直處於「山雨欲來風滿樓」的狀況，這是川普和共和黨在維護美國利益，藉此討好選民，為11月的國會選舉積攢支持度。而中國提出的制裁商品名單，也明顯是針對川普和共和黨票倉，短期內勢必對川普形成壓力。然而，他也指出，國會選舉並非美中關係緩和的時機，因為川普的真正目的在於「削減中國的競爭力」，貿易戰只是第一步。<br />\n<br />\n他分析，<span style=\"color: red;\">一旦度過國會選舉，川普和共和黨出於戰略考量，更有可能會放開手腳制裁中國，屆時將不僅針對貿易層面，連投資、尖端技術、中國發展模式，乃至中國體制方面，都將逐一處理。美對中的戰略圍堵，尤其針對「中國製造2025」計畫，將直接影響中國創新投資的環境，中國企業將沒辦法投資風險高的創新項目，這將是中國最大的損失。惟美方的問題在於，美國資本家不可能完全配合美國政府，切斷與中國的合作與聯繫。</span>"},{"pid":"cc9fe99f01d518209d350c2f5d7c81f38c74f9db","tid":706392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T23:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f503d7e9138f6911e2f61549af6821b9f1879433","tid":706392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:05:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a574ac20af9158ea257865ff4948d6bc93dbf754","tid":706392,"uid":67353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"__ __ 或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944f6f829e6f37a627cdf8dd09dafa3f642aeecf","tid":706392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ef78e0abfc5d52b1229e73e2c153499a46f23f","tid":706392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T01:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f0485ae1bdbf75405cf81a43a8573d2cb8193b","tid":706392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T03:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a18e5e994884a6e21147b39d5f0c79587e1aeb","tid":706392,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/19/134925_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F19%2F134925_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=ee1baa0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adbc81e3d843358f76d2155d410a1713e55cec46","tid":706392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}